spell_list.description: Enhances the troubador's defensive songs. Rank 1 allows Rejuvenating Celebration to increase maximum health by a percentage. Rank 2 allows Requiem of Reflection to increase the amount of health the group receives when healed. Rank 3 allows Graceful Avoidance to cost no concentration and increase the group's chance to dodge attacks.
spell_list.description_pvp: Enhances the troubador's defensive songs. Rank 1 allows Rejuvenating Celebration to increase maximum health by a percentage. Rank 2 allows Requiem of Reflection to increase the amount of health the group receives when healed. Rank 3 allows Graceful Avoidance to cost no concentration and increase the group's chance to dodge attacks.

effect_list.description: Graceful Avoidance will also grant a 3% chance to dodge attacks. It no longer costs concentration.
Requiem of Reflection will also increase the amount of health group members receive when healed by 5%.
Rejuvenating Celebration will also grant 5% maximum health to the group.

spell_list.name: Invigorating Ballad
